<reference id="resourceid" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>resourceid</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>resourceid</keyword>&gt; element provides an identifier for applications
that require them in a particular format, when the normal id attribute of
the topic can't be used. Each resourceid entry should be unique.
It is one of the metadata elements that can be included within the prolog
of a topic, along with document tracking and product information, etc. The
element has no content, but takes an <i>
         
         
         <keyword>id</keyword>
      
      
      </i> attribute or an <i>
         
         
         <keyword>appname</keyword>
      
      
      </i> attribute.</shortdesc>
   <prolog>
      <metadata>
         <keywords>
            <indexterm>resourceid</indexterm>
            <indexterm>Prolog
elements<indexterm>resourceid</indexterm>
            </indexterm>
            <indexterm>resourceid</indexterm>
         </keywords>
      </metadata>
   </prolog>
   <refbody>
      <refsyn>
         <title>Contained by</title>
         <xref href="prolog.xml">prolog</xref>
      </refsyn>
      <refsyn>
         <title>Contains</title> no content</refsyn>
      <section>
         <title>Attributes</title>
         <simpletable relcolwidth="2* 3* 1* 1* 1*" id="resourceid_attr">
            <sthead>
               <stentry>Name</stentry>
               <stentry>Description</stentry>
               <stentry>Data Type</stentry>
               <stentry>Default Value</stentry>
               <stentry>Required?</stentry>
            </sthead>
            <strow conref="commonLRdefs.xml#commonLRdefs/id">
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
            </strow>
            <strow conref="commonLRdefs.xml#commonLRdefs/appname">
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
            </strow>
            <strow conref="commonLRdefs.xml#commonLRdefs/global-atts">
               <stentry/>
